  "text": "The algorithm for the visualization of similar compounds has been adapted from the ToxRead model for mutagenicity, with some modifications necessary to deal with a continuous endpoint as the BCF rather than a categorical one, as described within the results section. The algorithm for measuring similarity is the same used within VEGA [CITATION_1] .",
